{"tid":663270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那雜種有咩用 一齊數下佢地既強項","createTime":"2018-05-13T07:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T08:49:06.000Z","uid":180258,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4028028db269e02223affc86bb085cf80f078213","tid":663270,"uid":180258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:12:11.000Z","msg":"支那人最叻:<br />\n-攞我地既資源<br />\n-爭學位<br />\n-炒樓，炒到咁撚高攪到我地啲香港人日做夜做做到狗咁就係為咗供首期<br />\n-爭公屋，攞綜緩，攞撚哂着數就拍拍屎忽走人<br />\n-偷呃拐騙<br />\n-乜撚都貪<br />\n-走水貨推高物價，提高香港人生活開支，市民生活受打擊<br />\n-講歪理<br />\n-覺得有錢大撚哂<br />\n<br />\n咁多強項 點鬥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(歡迎大家補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"721e14530095661ad1cbdd5672e092fde9d0f058","tid":663270,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T07:36:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"918b4cd7f9935501ee7f71eefd7786f222ad71c4","tid":663270,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:30:39.000Z","msg":"可以周街痾屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3087b0772f358f8bb5e5c27143768eccf3291082","tid":663270,"uid":123189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:32:21.000Z","msg":"炒樓 走水貨 講Y理呢d香港人都做緊"},{"pid":"914f03a3d3d37052054104debe63dc46cb628158","tid":663270,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:40:48.000Z","msg":"食囉 咩撚野都食得落"},{"pid":"258cc9d59c4ed46628af92fd5740267ea0c9ae9f","tid":663270,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T08:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bBqzLdw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FbBqzLdw.gif&h=c3496947&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}